<div id="wrapper"><h2><a href="/output/Page2.asp"><img alt="" height="70" src="../files/images/XM_logo.gif" title="XM London Digital Communication" width="162" /></a></h2><h2><img width="190" alt="Case histories" height="80" border="0" src="/files/images/XM_L3_Clients_histories_shdr.gif" /></h2><p><strong>SaBRE - Large Corporates</strong></p><p>SaBRE (Supporting Britain's Reservists and Employers) approached XM for an online solution to support their large corporate campaign. This campaign asked companies to sign-up to say they supported Britain's Reservist.</p><p>XM's solution was to redesign key pages within the site (including the homepage) to give a more friendly and corporate approach for its users. </p><p>To inform users about the objectives of the campaign, a splash page was created along with an 'About the campaign' page. The supportive companies listing page was also refreshed for easy navigation. </p><p>The end result saw 114 companies out of 340 sign-up to show their support for Reservists and an increase in the number of visitors to the site.</p><p><a href="http://www.sabre.mod.uk/" onclick="javascript:window.open('http://www.sabre.mod.uk/','_blank','scrollbars=yes,toolbar=yes,menubar=yes,resizable=yes,status=no,location=no,directories=no,width=600,height=800');return false;" target="_blank">http://www.sabre.mod.uk/</a></p><p><img alt="SaBRE Large Corporates" border="0" height="282" src="/files/images/SaBRE Large Corporates 1.jpg" width="275" /></p><p> </p><p><img alt="SaBRE Large Corporates" border="0" height="264" src="/files/images/SaBRE Large Corporates 2.jpg" width="275" /> </p><p> </p><p><img alt="SaBRE Large Corporates" border="0" height="322" src="/files/images/SaBRE Large Corporates 3.jpg" width="275" /></p><img class="hide" src="/files/images/clear.gif" width="1" height="1" alt="" />
